

 AI ROADMAP (FROM SCRATCH → PRO LEVEL)

 PHASE 0: Absolute Basics (2–4 weeks)



1. Programming (Python)

Learn:

Variables, loops, functions

Lists, dictionaries

File handling


Focus:  Write small programs daily (not just watching)


---

2. Math (only what you NEED)

Don’t panic—just core concepts:

Linear Algebra (vectors, matrices)

Probability basics

Basic calculus (derivatives intuition)



---

 PHASE 1: Logic Building (VERY IMPORTANT )

Do daily:

Solve 2–3 problems from:

Arrays

Strings

Basic recursion



Platforms:

LeetCode (easy level)

HackerRank


 Goal: Train your brain to think step-by-step


---

PHASE 2: Core AI + ML (1–2 months)

Learn Machine Learning concepts:

Supervised vs Unsupervised learning

Regression

Classification

Overfitting


Tools:

Python

NumPy

Pandas

Matplotlib

Scikit-learn



---

Build Projects (THIS is where most people fail)

Don’t just learn—build:

Start with:

1. House price predictor


2. Student score predictor


3. Spam email classifier



 Even simple projects = HUGE confidence boost


---

PHASE 3: Deep Learning (Next Level)

Learn:

Neural Networks

Forward + Backpropagation

Activation functions


Tools:

TensorFlow or PyTorch


Projects:

Image classifier

Digit recognizer

Basic chatbot



---

 PHASE 4: Specialization (Pick ONE)

Don’t try everything. Choose your lane:

1. AI + Healthcare (Perfect for your project)

Disease prediction

Medical imaging


2. NLP (Chatbots, AI assistants)

Text classification

Sentiment analysis


3. Computer Vision

Face detection

Object detection



---

 PHASE 5: Real-World Skills

Learn:

Git + GitHub 
APIs
Model deployment


Tools:

Flask / FastAPI

Streamlit (easy UI)






One real-world problem project











Golden Rule:

 If you don’t build, you don’t learn AI

 DAILY PLAN (REALISTIC)


1 hr → Coding practice (logic)

1 hr → Learning concept

1 hr → Building project



